 offers 24 hour support via +1 716-745-HOST and through our custom Control Panel <a href=\"https://shp.servermania.com/user/login\">https://shp.servermania.com</a>.</p><p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>&nbsp;Network tests</strong></p><p>Buffalo, NY, USA: 192.157.59.250<br>\nLos Angeles, CA, USA: 23.229.123.150</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fblack-friday-servermania-7month-1gb-xen-hvm-windows-vps-in-los-angeles-and-buffalo%2F&amp;t=%5BBLACK%20FRIDAY%5D%20ServerMania%20-%20%247%2Fmonth%201GB%20Xen-HVM%20Windows%20VPS%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20Buffalo\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=%5BBLACK%20FRIDAY%5D%20ServerMania%20-%20%247%2Fmonth%201GB%20Xen-HVM%20Windows%20VPS%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20Buffalo&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fblack-friday-servermania-7month-1gb-xen-hvm-windows-vps-in-los-angeles-and-buffalo%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-twitter dpsp-no-label\" title=\"Share on Twitter\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fblack-friday-servermania-7month-1gb-xen-hvm-windows-vps-in-los-angeles-and-buffalo%2F&amp;title=%5BBLACK%20FRIDAY%5D%